fr.upem.jShell.Eval

Class SnippetEval

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.upem.jShell.Eval.SnippetEval

  • public class SnippetEval
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class for using jShell. It provides two methods for testing pieces of code. It is the only class aware of jShell existence.
